From: Gabrielle Ferguson <gferguson@msra.org.au>
Sent: Tuesday, April 28, 2020 4:45:42 PM
To: Petricia Augustus <paugustus@msra.org.au>
Subject: MS Research Australia Brain Bank Web Page

Hi Trish!

Hope you are well 😊

I have been experiencing this bizarre issue with the MSRABB Website- we are getting frequently spammed via the Donor EOI online form.

They have been steadily increasing to the point where we get around 4 a day. They are all similar (they all come from the city of Minsk) and use random English words,

I've attached a screenshot below as an example.

Who would I contact to look into blocking these spams? I have spoken to Centrix, and they weren't sure, neither was Rob D'Arrigo but he did mention a company called Wolf IQ?

Let me know what you think 😊

Gabrielle
